'''沙特阿拉伯王國'''（{{lang-ar|المملكة العربية السعودية}}，''{{transl|ar|al-Mamlakah ʿArabīyah as-Saʿūdīyah}}''，{{smaller|{{audio|Ar-Kingdom Saudi Arabia.oga|发音}}}}），简称'''沙特阿拉伯'''、'''沙特'''（{{lang-ar|العربية السعودية}}），或譯-{zh-cn:'''沙乌地阿拉伯'''、'''沙地阿拉伯''';zh-tw:'''沙特阿拉伯'''、'''沙地阿拉伯''';zh-hk:'''沙特阿拉伯'''、'''沙烏地阿拉伯''';zh-my:'''沙乌地阿拉伯'''、'''沙特阿拉伯''';zh-sg:'''沙乌地阿拉伯'''、'''沙地阿拉伯''';}-<ref>也曾译作“蘇地亞拉伯”，见1945年[https://treaties.un.org/doc/publication/ctc/uncharter.pdf 联合国宪章] {{Wayback|url=https://treaties.un.org/doc/publication/ctc/uncharter.pdf |date=20180225202219 }}</ref>，是一個位於[[西亞|西亞]][[阿拉伯半島|阿拉伯半島]]的[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]][[國家|國家]]。沙特阿拉伯面積2,149,690平方公里，是在[[阿拉伯世界|阿拉伯世界]]中地理面積第二大的國家，僅次於[[阿爾及利亞|阿爾及利亞]]。沙地阿拉伯北方與[[約旦|約旦]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]接壤；東北與[[科威特|科威特]]接壤；東邊和[[卡塔爾|卡塔爾]]、[[巴林|巴林]]及[[阿拉伯聯合酋長國|阿拉伯聯合酋長國]]交界；東南方和[[阿曼|阿曼]]接壤；南方則與[[也門|也門]]交界。它是唯一一個同時擁有[[紅海|紅海]]和[[波斯灣|波斯灣]][[海岸線|海岸線]]的國家，大部分的土地由不宜居的沙漠及貧瘠的荒野組成。現時沙地阿拉伯由四個本來分明的區域——[[汉志_(沙特阿拉伯)|漢志]]、[[內志|內志]]、部分[[東阿拉伯半島|東阿拉伯半島]]和部分{{le|南阿拉伯半島|South Arabia}}組成<ref>{{cite book|author=Madawi Al-Rasheed|title=A Most Masculine State: Gender, Politics and Religion in Saudi Arabia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JmafWmVNJAAC&pg=PA65&dq|year=2013|page=65|access-date=2015-09-26|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906120802/https://books.google.com/books?id=JmafWmVNJAAC&pg=PA65&dq|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

沙烏地阿拉伯王國是於1932年由[[伊本·沙特|伊本·沙特]]成立，他由1902年奪回[[沙特王朝|沙特王朝]]歷史領地[[利雅得|利雅得]]開始，相繼[[沙特阿拉伯统一|以征服統一]]了以上的四個區域，該國從此便一直以根據[[伊斯蘭主义|伊斯蘭主义]]原則、以[[君主專制|君主專制]]的形式统治。[[瓦哈比派|瓦哈比派]]这一被定為国教的极端保守[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]派别亦被稱為「沙特文化的首要特徵」，并随着其政策在全世界范围内传播<ref name="HT2003: 14">[[#HT2003|Tripp, ''Culture Shock'', 2003]]: p.14</ref><ref>[[#Malbouisson|Malbouisson]], p. 23</ref>。沙地阿拉伯有時被稱為「兩聖寺之地」，因为它的範圍包括了伊斯蘭教中兩個最神聖的聖地：[[麥加|麥加]]的[[禁寺|禁寺]]及[[麥地那|麥地那]]的[[先知寺|先知寺]]。作为一个政治上極端保守，并採用[[政教合一|政教合一]]体制的[[独裁|独裁]]政權<ref name="EIU">{{cite book|title=Democracy index 2012 Democracy at a standstill|date=2012|publisher=The Economist Intelligence Unit|url=http://pages.eiu.com/rs/eiu2/images/Democracy-Index-2012.pdf|access-date=2015-09-26|archive-date=2017-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320185156/http://pages.eiu.com/rs/eiu2/images/Democracy-Index-2012.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，沙特阿拉伯对{{le|沙特阿拉伯女性權利|Women's rights in Saudi Arabia|女性權利}}的限制极多<ref>[http://www.theweek.co.uk/60339/eleven-things-women-in-saudi-arabia-cannot-do Six things women in Saudi Arabia cannot do] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theweek.co.uk/60339/eleven-things-women-in-saudi-arabia-cannot-do |date=20151206195436 }} The Week 2017-09-27</ref>，隨著下一代國王即位後近年來不平等現象已經較為緩和，但仍采用[[酷刑|酷刑]]和[[沙烏地阿拉伯死刑制度|残忍的死刑行刑方法]]<ref name="UNComdemn">{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/1992027.stm |title=BBC news: Saudi 'torture' condemned by UN |website=BBC |language=en |date= |accessdate=2008-03-23 |archive-date=2008-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080308162124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/1992027.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

沙地阿拉伯是世界上石油生產量及[[各国石油出口量列表|輸出量]]最高的國家，它同時控制了全球第二大的[[各国石油储量列表|烴儲藏量]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=International - U.S. Energy Information Administration (EIA)|url=https://www.eia.gov/beta/international/?view=production|accessdate=2019-12-31|work=www.eia.gov|archive-date=2020-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117024143/https://www.eia.gov/beta/international/?view=production|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於石化燃料产业支持經濟发展，沙地阿拉伯被列為[[高收入經濟體|高收入經濟體]]之一，[[人類發展指數|人類發展指數]]亦極高<ref name="UNDR2014">{{cite book|title=Human Development Report 2014|date=2013|publisher=United Nations|page=159|url=http://hdr.undp.org/sites/default/files/hdr14-report-en-1.pdf|access-date=2014-12-06|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018115808/http://hdr.undp.org/sites/default/files/hdr14-report-en-1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且是唯一在[[二十國集團|二十國集團]]中的阿拉伯國家<ref>{{cite book|author=James Wynbrandt|title=A Brief History of Saudi Arabia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=99M0zoSqsF0C&pg=PA242|year=2004|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=978-1-4381-0830-8|page=242|access-date=2015-09-26|archive-date=2015-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906133618/https://books.google.com/books?id=99M0zoSqsF0C&pg=PA242|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Saudi Arabia to overtake Russia as top oil producer-IEA |author=Soldatkin, Vladimir; Astrasheuskaya, Nastassia |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/11/09/russia-energy-iea-idUSL6E7M93XT20111109 |agency=Reuters |date=2011-11-09 |accessdate=2015-09-26 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924160408/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/11/09/russia-energy-iea-idUSL6E7M93XT20111109 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是，它在[[海灣阿拉伯國家合作委員會|海灣阿拉伯國家合作委員會]]成員中擁有最單一的經濟<ref>{{cite web|title=UAE has most diversified GCC economy|url=http://www.emirates247.com/business/economy-finance/uae-has-most-diversified-gcc-economy-2014-01-06-1.533612|work=emirates247.com|date=2014-01-06|accessdate=2015-09-26|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924000538/http://www.emirates247.com/business/economy-finance/uae-has-most-diversified-gcc-economy-2014-01-06-1.533612|dead-url=no}}</ref>。沙地阿拉伯的[[各国国防预算列表|國防開支]]在世界排行第四<ref>[http://www.iiss.org/en/about%20us/press%20room/press%20releases/press%20releases/archive/2014-dd03/february-0abc/military-balance-2014-press-statement-52d7 The Military Balance 2014: Top 15 Defence Budgets 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iiss.org/en/about%20us/press%20room/press%20releases/press%20releases/archive/2014-dd03/february-0abc/military-balance-2014-press-statement-52d7 |date=20150924033509 }} (IISS)</ref><ref name="SIPRI">{{cite web |url = http://books.sipri.org/product_info?c_product_id=476 |title = The 15 countries with the highest military expenditure in 2013 (table) |publisher = [[Stockholm_International_Peace_Research_Institute|Stockholm International Peace Research Institute]] |format = PDF |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150104033821/http://books.sipri.org/product_info?c_product_id=476 |archivedate = 2015-01-04 }}</ref>，在2010至2014年曾被[[斯德哥爾摩國際和平研究所|斯德哥爾摩國際和平研究所]]列为世界第二大軍備进口者<ref name="books.sipri.org">{{cite web|title=Trends in International Arms Transfer, 2014|url=http://books.sipri.org/product_info?c_product_id=495|website=www.sipri.org|publisher=Stockholm International Peace Research Institute|accessdate=2015-03-18|ref=SIPRI Fact Sheet, March 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319023856/http://books.sipri.org/product_info?c_product_id=495|archivedate=2015-03-19}}</ref>。它常被视為[[地域大國|地域大國]]和[[中等強國|中等強國]]<ref name="The United States and the Great Powers">{{cite book | author =Barry Buzan | title=The United States and the Great Powers | publisher=Polity Press | year=2004 | location=Cambridge, United Kingdom | pages =71 | isbn =0-7456-3375-7}}</ref>。除了[[海灣阿拉伯國家合作委員會|海灣阿拉伯國家合作委員會]]，它亦是[[伊斯蘭合作組織|伊斯蘭合作組織]]和[[石油输出国组织|石油輸出國家組織]]的成員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.middleeastmonitor.com/articles/middle-east/8207-the-erosion-of-saudi-arabias-image-among-its-neighbours |title=The erosion of Saudi Arabia's image among its neighbours |publisher=Middleeastmonitor.com |date=2013-11-07 |accessdate=2015-09-26 |archive-date=2015-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908130728/https://www.middleeastmonitor.com/articles/middle-east/8207-the-erosion-of-saudi-arabias-image-among-its-neighbours |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

